result_quotes: OK, do his tonsils look enlarged?
Uh, everything looks swollen in there, I don't know what's what, but it does look very angry in there.
OK, have you noticed any swelling in in the neck area?
Uhm, I think there might be like a few lumps near his neck, so I don't know if that's swelling, but definitely there is. There's a few that I felt over the last few days.
And is he having any issues swallowing food or fluids?
Yeah, it seems like appetite's gone down, like a lot of pain in his throat, especially when swallowing solid foods.
Have you taken a look into his throat? Is it red? Do you see any yellow streaking white stuff, anything like that?
I definitely did take a look yesterday and definitely saw a lot of redness. I don't know if I saw any white or yellow streaks, but definitely looks very red in there.
